gh mobility of such mesoscopic twin boundaries\noriginates from their diffuse nature which renders pinning by atomistic point\ndefects ineffective.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2010 16:12:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2011 14:00:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-21"}
