here-cap-quantized-CSI model, this policy is shown to perform water-filling\nover feedback links. Finally, simulation demonstrates that feedback-control\nyields significant throughput gains compared with the conventional\ndifferential-feedback method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Dec 2010 09:11:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Aug 2011 16:54:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2012 04:01:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
